<AUTHOR>jprich</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>My first new car. Read a lot of reviews. Had a great deal (rebate) + winter tires and other free goodies. Had it for 5 months and nearly 10k km on it. Went on a trip to Boston from Montreal and the car ran perfectly well. Very comfortable and roomy. Gas mileage on road is greater than expected. Bit disappointed for city mileage though. Had a burned tail light and the small door speaker unglued itself on the first month but got them fixed right away. No biggies. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>6 Speakers system + USB/IPOD = AWESOME. Good gaz mileage on road. Mixed leather/cloth seats is a great idea. Very large trunk.</FAVORITE>
