<AUTHOR>bmac50</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Less then 1400 miles, one of the first things I did was change the air filter to K&N, seeing 23 MPG in town, on the road I don't know yet but some mixed with mostly town 26. More than enough pick up to get out of the way and starting in 1st. Very roomy, good seats and driving position, wish the seat bottom was a little longer but on any car I do. Easy to read gauges, very strong brakes and great audio system. Of course the best warranty in the business doesn't hurt. Easy to get the steering wheel where you like with both tilt and telescopic. Wasn't really that hot about leather or the moon roof but I'm finding I was quite wrong.</TEXT>
